From: Dr. Oscar P. Larghi <oplarghi@drwebsa.com.ar>

I apologize for having missed a zero for the dog population of Tarlac. As
cited by the Manila Times, this population is estimated in aprox. 208 000
dogs; this many doses of vaccine would cost US$50,000.
